The paper proposes a behavioral equivalence for feature transition systems (FTS) and presents a minimization algorithm for a restricted notion of coherent branching feature bisimulation. This work is relevant to the areas of software engineering, programming languages, formal methods, and logic. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), followed by cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.PL (Programming Languages), cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory), and cs.LT (Logic in Computer Science).
